  "content": "<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center\">Cartier Women's Initiative Award Programs</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-8\">\n                {/* Regional Awards - North America */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center mb-2\">\n                      <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Regional Awards - North America</h3>\n                    </div>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                      <div>\n                        <h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3 text-purple-800\">Award Structure</h4>\n                        <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n                          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between bg-purple-50 p-3 rounded-lg\">\n                            <span class=\"font-semibold\">1st Place:</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-purple-700 font-bold\">$100,000</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between bg-purple-50 p-3 rounded-lg\">\n                            <span class=\"font-semibold\">2nd Place:</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-purple-700 font-bold\">$60,000</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between bg-purple-50 p-3 rounded-lg\">\n                            <span class=\"font-semibold\">3rd Place:</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-purple-700 font-bold\">$30,000</span>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3 text-gray-800\">Fellowship Benefits</h4>\n                        <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2\">\n                          <p><strong>Coaching:</strong> Tailored mentoring and executive coaching</p>\n                          <p><strong>Education:</strong> INSEAD business school courses</p>\n                          <p><strong>Visibility:</strong> Global media exposure and recognition</p>\n                          <p><strong>Network:</strong> Global fellows community connections</p>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"mt-6 p-4 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg\">\n                      <h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">📋 North America Region Details:</h5>\n                      <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm\">\n                        <div>\n                          <ul class=\"space-y-1\">\n                            <li>• <strong>Coverage:</strong> Canada, United States, Mexico</li>\n                            <li>• <strong>Duration:</strong> January-December 2027 fellowship</li>\n                            <li>• <strong>In-Person:</strong> 1 week event April/May 2027</li>\n                          </ul>\n                        </div>\n                        <div>\n                          <ul class=\"space-y-1\">\n                            <li>• <strong>Time Commitment:</strong> 1-3 hours/week</li>\n                            <li>• <strong>Impact Reporting:</strong> 3 years post-fellowship</li>\n                            <li>• <strong>Filming:</strong> On-site business documentation</li>\n                          </ul>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                {/* Science & Technology Pioneer Award */}\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-center mb-2\">\n                      <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">Science & Technology Pioneer Award</h3>\n                    </div>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                      <div>\n                        <h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3 text-blue-800\">Deep Tech Ventures</h4>\n                        <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n                          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg\">\n                            <span class=\"font-semibold\">Award Amount:</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-blue-700 font-bold\">$100K/$60K/$30K</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1\">\n                            <p>• Deep tech businesses based on pioneering technology</p>\n                            <p>• Complex engineering processes or scientific discoveries</p>\n                            <p>• Not just disruptive business models</p>\n                            <p>• Same fellowship benefits as Regional Awards</p>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h4 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3 text-gray-800\">Ideal Candidates</h4>\n                        <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2\">\n                          <p><strong>Technology:</strong> Pioneering new technology development</p>\n                          <p><strong>Scientific:</strong> Based on scientific discoveries</p>\n                          <p><strong>Engineering:</strong> Complex engineering innovations</p>\n                          <p><strong>Impact:</strong> Addresses UN SDGs through deep tech</p>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n",
